Organizers of Africa’s popular reality TV show, Big Brother Naija (BBNaija), have announced that the 2022 Season 7 edition will premiere on Saturday 23rd and 24th of July 2022. The organizers, in a press briefing on Tuesday, said the new season will premiere across all DSTV packages on channel 198 and on GOtv Max and Plus on channel 29. It also announced that the winner will walk away with N100 million worth of prizes and housemates will be in the house for 72 days. “The winner for #BBNaijaS7 goes home with N100,000,000. N50,000,000 in cash and N50,000,000 worth of prizes from sponsors.” It also added that with no more COVID-19 restrictions, therefore, there will be a live audience and ninja.